BT /F2 11 Tf 50 675 Td (1. Purpose & Scope) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 657 Td (Defines authorization and tracking requirements for all physical access to Safaricom) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 50 644 Td (Ethiopia network sites by internal staff, contractors, and third-party vendors.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 623 Td (2. Access Categories) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 605 Td (• Internal Staff: Requires valid employee ID and site access badge.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 592 Td (• Contractors: Require approved work order and signed NDA on file.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 579 Td (• Vendors/OEM: Require pre-approved vendor access form and escort by NOC engineer.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 558 Td (3. Pre-Access Authorization) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 540 Td (• Submit site access request via NOC portal minimum 24 hours in advance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 527 Td (• NOC supervisor approves request and issues time-bound access code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 514 Td (• Security team notified with expected arrival window and personnel list.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 493 Td (4. On-Site Check-In) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 475 Td (• Register at site security checkpoint with photo ID and access code.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 462 Td (• Log entry time, purpose, equipment carried, and contact number.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 449 Td (• Collect site key from NOC duty engineer for secured equipment rooms.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 428 Td (5. During Site Visit) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 410 Td (• Notify NOC L1 operator immediately upon arrival at equipment area.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 397 Td (• All equipment changes must be coordinated with NOC in real-time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 384 Td (• No unauthorized power cycling of active network equipment permitted.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 371 Td (• Maintain communication with NOC via mobile phone throughout visit.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 50 350 Td (6. Site Departure) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 332 Td (• Log departure time in the site access register.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 319 Td (• Return all keys and access cards to designated NOC contact.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 306 Td (• Notify NOC L1 operator upon safe departure from site.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 60 293 Td (• Submit site visit report within 4 hours if any issues encountered.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 50 30 Td (CONFIDENTIAL — For internal NOC use only. Safaricom Ethiopia PLC.) Tj ET
